snippet.title: Bootleg Soldier Azure: ASTRAL RAVE
snippet.description:
Help one-time wonder Yuuto Ichika in her quest to get her cookbook back while shooting down everything that tries to stop her in this fast-paced shoot 'em up, featuring a 2 stage story mode and a 3 minute caravan mode!

Made in a month for Magical Girl Game Jam #9!

Get it on itch.io for free here: https://crows-nest.itch.io/bootleg-soldier-azure-astral-rave

This game contains arrangements of songs originally composed by Princess Sylvysprit: https://www.youtube.com/c/princesssylvysprit
